## Key Characteristics

| Aspect | Trunk-Based Dev |
|--------|-----------------|
| **Main Branch** | Always production-ready |
| **Branch Duration** | < 1 day (ideally hours) |
| **Commit Frequency** | Multiple times per day |
| **Code Review** | Pre-commit or post-merge |
| **CI/CD** | Mandatory & automated |
| **Testing** | Extensive (unit, integration) |
| **Feature Control** | Feature flags/toggles |

## Implementation Strategies

### 1. Direct Commits to Main
```bash
git checkout main
git pull origin main
# Make small changes
git add .
git commit -m "feat: add user profile endpoint"
git push origin main
```

### 2. Short-Lived Feature Branches
```bash
git checkout -b feature/quick-fix
# Work for hours (not days)
git commit -m "fix: memory leak in cache"
git push origin feature/quick-fix
# Merge immediately via fast-forward
```

### 3. Feature Flags for Incomplete Features
```javascript
if (featureFlags.isEnabled('newPaymentSystem')) {
    // Use new payment system
    return newPaymentProcessor();
} else {
    // Use existing system
    return oldPaymentProcessor();
}
```

